on. Nearly 350 terms have been added, and new definitions for many of the original terms supplied. Excellent diagrammatic line drawings by Henry A. C. Jackson illustrate 191 of the terms.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aMicologia. 0aMycology. 0aMykologie. 0aPflanzen (Botanik). 4aMycology -- Dictionaries. 4aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Botany. 4aSCIENCE / Reference. 7aSCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aDick, Esther A., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aJackson, Henry A. C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP e-dition: Complete eBook Packagez9783110353488oZDB-23-HCO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP e-dition: Science eBook Packagez9783110353549oZDB-23-HSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z97831104422120 cprintz978067443552040uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/harvard.978067443553740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674435537423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674435537/original  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-HCO  aZDB-23-HSP